 a hidden boss. Also, yeah, he’s totally named after the band Pink Floyd. - Samuel Moreno \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/mortal-kombat-1-pink-floyd-secret-boss-how-to-beat-1851766330?_gl=1*1xi7nht*_ga*MTc0MjY2NTg1OS4xNzQwMzc1OTc4*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTc0MDc2NTY5Ni4xNy4xLjE3NDA3NzA4MDkuNjAuMC4w\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/mortal-kombat-1-pink-floyd-secret-boss-how-to-beat-1851766330?_gl=1*1xi7nht*_ga*MTc0MjY2NTg1OS4xNzQwMzc1OTc4*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTc0MDc2NTY5Ni4xNy4xLjE3NDA3NzA4MDkuNjAuMC4w\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"b34c07a284f57dcb56fa6c1c27ad420e\" data-recommend-id=\"image://b34c07a284f57dcb56fa6c1c27ad420e\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"An image of the Darkrai ex card from Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"An image of the Darkrai ex card from Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/b34c07a284f57dcb56fa6c1c27ad420e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/b34c07a284f57dcb56fa6c1c27ad420e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/b34c07a284f57dcb56fa6c1c27ad420e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"An image 